<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:01:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国恒大电动汽车子公司进入破产重组程序</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-evergrandes-ev-arm-units-enter-bankruptcy-reorganization-proceedings-2024-08-05/</link><description>中国恒大新能源汽车周一表示，在该公司的两个子公司的个人债权人提出破产程序一周后，当地法院已裁定该公司的两个子公司应进入破产并进行重组。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:24:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-evergrandes-ev-arm-units-enter-bankruptcy-reorganization-proceedings-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警在萨宾娜浅滩监视菲律宾巡逻艇</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-monitors-philippine-patrol-boats-sabina-shoal-2024-08-05/</link><description>中国海警表示，正在监视聚集在有争议的萨比纳浅滩周围的菲律宾巡逻船和渔船，并称中国对南海的南沙群岛拥有“无可争议的主权”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:02:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-monitors-philippine-patrol-boats-sabina-shoal-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国经济衰退风险拖累股市，债券押注快速降息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-04/</link><description>周一，亚洲股市下跌，债券上涨，原因是对美国可能陷入衰退的担忧引发了大规模的避险情绪，押注利率将不得不大幅下降，以支持经济增长。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 23:37:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-04/</guid></item><item><title>早申：再见软着陆，你好紧急着陆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-04/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 21:52:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-04/</guid></item><item><title>美国预计将提议禁止自动驾驶汽车使用中国软件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-expected-propose-barring-chinese-software-autonomous-vehicles-2024-08-04/</link><description>据知情人士透露，美国商务部预计将在未来几周内提议禁止在自动驾驶和联网汽车中使用中国软件。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 21:26:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-expected-propose-barring-chinese-software-autonomous-vehicles-2024-08-04/</guid></item><item><title>游泳：中国队终结美国对男子4×100米混合泳接力的统治</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/swimming-china-end-us-reign-over-mens-4x100-medley-relay-2024-08-04/</link><description>中国游泳运动员因兴奋剂指控而受到审查。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 17:29:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/swimming-china-end-us-reign-over-mens-4x100-medley-relay-2024-08-04/</guid></item><item><title>羽毛球：台湾选手李、王卫冕男双金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/badminton-taiwans-lee-wang-beat-china-win-mens-doubles-gold-2024-08-04/</link><description>周日，台湾选手李扬/王齐麟在拉夏贝尔体育馆举行的一场扣人心弦的决赛中以21-17 18-21 21-19击败中国选手梁伟铿/王昶，卫冕奥运会羽毛球男双冠军。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 15:53:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/badminton-taiwans-lee-wang-beat-china-win-mens-doubles-gold-2024-08-04/</guid></item><item><title>台湾庆祝羽毛球战胜中国大陆，但没有政治象征</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/badminton-taiwan-supporters-checked-political-symbols-final-with-china-2024-08-04/</link><description>周日，台湾支持者在没有国旗的情况下举行的巴黎奥运会羽毛球双打决赛中庆祝了台湾在巴黎奥运会上获得的第一枚金牌，安保人员执行了国际奥委会的规定。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 15:44:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/badminton-taiwan-supporters-checked-political-symbols-final-with-china-2024-08-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国队凭借刘洋扣环夺得期待已久的金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-china-take-one-two-rings-with-liu-retaining-title-2024-08-04/</link><description>周日，刘洋在吊环决赛中大展拳脚，成功卫冕奥运冠军，为中国队在巴黎奥运会上赢得了期待已久的首枚体操金牌。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 14:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-china-take-one-two-rings-with-liu-retaining-title-2024-08-04/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球：中国范冰冰夺得男单金牌，法国小将勒布伦获得铜牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/table-tennis-chinas-fan-wins-table-tennis-gold-mens-singles-swede-moregard-2024-08-04/</link><description>中国选手范振东周日在奥运会男子乒乓球单打决赛中击败瑞典选手特鲁斯·莫加德，弥补了三年前在东京错失的金牌。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 13:30:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/table-tennis-chinas-fan-wins-table-tennis-gold-mens-singles-swede-moregard-2024-08-04/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜表示俄罗斯普京就洪水破坏提供了人道主义援助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-says-russias-putin-offered-humanitarian-aid-over-flood-damage-2024-08-03/</link><description>大雨袭击了朝鲜西北部地区，4000多所房屋被淹，约5000名居民被隔离</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 22:35:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-says-russias-putin-offered-humanitarian-aid-over-flood-damage-2024-08-03/</guid></item><item><title>网球：郑智击败维克奇为中国队夺得历史性金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/tennis-zheng-beats-vekic-win-historic-gold-china-2024-08-03/</link><description>郑沁文在周六紧张的决赛中以6-2 6-3击败克罗地亚选手唐娜·维克奇，成为首位获得奥运会网球单打金牌的中国选手。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 16:41:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/tennis-zheng-beats-vekic-win-historic-gold-china-2024-08-03/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球：中国选手陈再次击败队友孙卫冕女单冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-chen-beats-teammate-sun-again-defend-womens-singles-title-2024-08-03/</link><description>周六，中国卫冕冠军陈梦在巴黎奥运会上以4比2击败队友孙颖莎，夺得乒乓球女单金牌，就像她在东京奥运会上取得的成绩一样，历史重演。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 15:01:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-chen-beats-teammate-sun-again-defend-womens-singles-title-2024-08-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国西南地区洪水、泥石流造成2人死亡，房屋、桥梁被毁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/floods-mudslides-kill-2-southwest-china-destroy-homes-bridge-2024-08-03/</link><description>据官方媒体周六报道，周六，洪水和泥石流摧毁了中国西南省份四川省的村庄房屋和部分高速公路，两起事件造成至少两人死亡、17 人失踪。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 06:30:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/floods-mudslides-kill-2-southwest-china-destroy-homes-bridge-2024-08-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国就军舰进入台海向加拿大提出投诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-filed-complaints-with-canada-over-warship-taiwan-strait-2024-08-02/</link><description>中国国防部周五表示，加拿大军舰穿越台湾海峡后，中国已通过军事和外交渠道向加拿大提出投诉。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 10:58:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-filed-complaints-with-canada-over-warship-taiwan-strait-2024-08-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>